######## tmux ----------------------------> new alternative for screen

below are the commands

#########

tmux  ----> create new session
tmux a    ---> attach session
tmux list-sesssions   -----> list session that are running
tmux a -t 0 ---->    tmux attach the session
ctrl + b d --> to detach the session
ctrl b % ----> split the windows in multiple tabs
ctrl b q ----> to display the split windows number
ctrl b q 1 -----> give number to jump to that session
Resize Panes in tmux :
Press Ctrl + b, then press : to bring up the command prompt.

Resize down: resize-pane -D (for moving the border down)

Resize up: resize-pane -U (for moving the border up)

Resize left: resize-pane -L (for moving the border left)

Resize right: resize-pane -R (for moving the border right)





